{
  "stem": "10960.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- happened happened up to now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Shall I say during the time when we were occupied with the Russians or shall I skip before the-- before the-- you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I-- OK, being at school, at the medical school, we heard in 1941 that it's a spectacle we're having.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we got-- were occupied by the Russians since 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, Poland was occupied by the Russians in 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and we-- we heard that a lot of trucks were sent from Russia to pick up the Jews who are willing to leave Poland to Russia.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Many of them went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, they did suffer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of them suffered a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of them were sent to Siberia and this and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was already pregnant, so I was afraid to go on trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They say that trucks-- I was thinking to myself, and we remained in-- as the bombs were falling already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were living in [INAUDIBLE] of '45 in Rowne and-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] and the-- the Germans occupied us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Didn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We heard we have a Judenrat was-- was announced on-- on the post-- post.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Jews cannot walk without the yellow Magen David star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Jews are not allowed to walk on the street until at least they-- if they have jobs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And so we were in-- in the houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We-- we had a-- we started to get bad feelings, scaredness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they hear-- we-- anything what we want to know, we shall go to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
